expression: stdout
---
Detect bloated notes and suggest refactoring

Usage: obsidian-cli-inspector analyze bloat [OPTIONS]

Options:
  -t, --threshold <THRESHOLD>  Minimum size threshold in bytes [default: 50000]
  -l, --limit <LIMIT>          Maximum number of notes to analyze [default: 10]
  -o, --output <FORMAT>        Output in JSON format (for machine integration)
  -h, --help                   Print help
